/> 成日慢鏡完都射唔撚中"},{"pid":"40a3d123d75f7e1b9f4e5ef100988e6e8e21b904","tid":256797,"uid":56657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T01:51:54.000Z","msg":"冇時間既話horizon,  nier劇情較長<br />\n但強烈推介2隻都玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhorizon畫面勝<br />\nnier人設音樂勝<br />\n劇情唔洗講，2隻都正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c287f3286d44c8918e64f390d9f61e1d0cfcf184","tid":256797,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"好肯定投的人好多都唔係玩哂2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我冇玩過zero dawn 唔會投"},{"pid":"92c0bea267df71faa5736aa55b3cf89650e58460","tid":256797,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Horizon 如果唔係玩手制一定好玩好多<br />\nNieR劇情真係屈機 不過遊戲性一般 打鬥上唔洗用咩技巧</blockquote><br />\n玩開pc槍game，一開始玩ps4搞到個主角小兒麻痹咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36f5136b9e940c0b07692d2a5ddcff6a30522bd","tid":256797,"uid":50351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:11:26.000Z","msg":"Horizon機械獸種類太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但畫面真係好正，故事都正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNier賣劇情，戰鬥系統流暢但無挑戰性<br />\n除非開極難唔係都係無雙<br />\n兩隻都係值得玩既驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申兩隻玩哂，覺得唔需要分高低"},{"pid":"0674cc9f135d78f1393255953bd6a227d0676122","tid":256797,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:31:15.000Z","msg":"兩隻都係必玩佳作<br />\n冇時間係有絕症定移民冇電用既地方<br />\n最多分早玩遲玩"},{"pid":"a0e191c46b724f64c3c52681af4839da8aa07c55","tid":256797,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:38:28.000Z","msg":"Nier 配樂係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711f066fe6541bdb86a7207d00dddf14d52d7820","tid":256797,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"horizon戰鬥有d麻煩 子彈都難搞到手<br />\n<br />\n但畫面堅掂 初初到子午城睇到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dac8ee3a30eedde191e36ef78f309e4e3772d4","tid":256797,"uid":30417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:51:31.000Z","msg":"Horizon zero dawn 就戰鬥上好玩啲，因為唔同怪有唔同弱點，又有多啲唔同種類武器同陷阱用，可以諗吓戰術。另外畫面超靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而 NieR:Automata 就劇情上好啲，俾玩家多啲反思/思考空間，比較容易投入劇情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  另外人設同音樂都超正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結論係兩隻 game 都好正，樓主買哂佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8a80e79cf68373925806f486aa3ee7d8832f8a","tid":256797,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"Horizon後期唔多掂 所有怪基本上冰完就炸"},{"pid":"fe1e5486480002de741542ecd68b8f5966868c1c","tid":256797,"uid":46588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Horizon後期唔多掂 所有怪基本上冰完就炸</blockquote><br />\nhorizon後期主角太高攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be79b559eda41c4a84070d97400f90de6d80a92","tid":256797,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"兩隻都玩左<br />\nNier個腦玩完要沈澱，有啲幾stunning既message比玩家<br />\nHorizon就好靚，個故都幾好既，不過幾淺白<br />\n要玩一隻我揀nier"},{"pid":"565f53cf04f83ddc3ff9e2d38e41034f27f2331b","tid":256797,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"仁王"},{"pid":"7d9c4ac7a993c498a7d23280953eafafb983e183","tid":256797,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:38:09.000Z","msg":"兩隻都好撚正"},{"pid":"6dc152cfad7b52a2bbaeb876373453f5ba242a93","tid":256797,"uid":30417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Horizon後期唔多掂 所有怪基本上冰完就炸</blockquote><br />\nhorizon後期主角太高攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有織盾者甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463ca25ea74f19f1df84bf82a1267ab363138604","tid":256797,"uid":616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:03:48.000Z","msg":"劇情既話我會揀nier<br />\n<br />\n整體遊戲性就會揀horizon<br />\n<br />\n睇個人選擇<br />\n<br />\nNier遊戲系統真心麻麻，但劇情同音樂就世界級，當佢rpg玩就無得輸，遊戲性就真係無乜特別，d打鬥太單調<br />\n<br />\nHorizon開始玩就好正個遊戲性，不過玩到後期d野重複性極高，不過後期個劇情都唔錯，算佳作，不過去唔到神作，因為每樣野都唔算完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}